AI-NeuralNet-FastSOM
====================

A mostly drop-in replacement for AI::NeuralNet::SOM, but faster.

Really, just a shameless rip of Robert Barta's code with most of the
heavy lifting moved to C.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires a working C compiler.

